 "remarks": "Classic 5-bedroom center hall Colonial nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac in one of Darien&apos;s most convenient locations, just a short walk to school. Beautifully sited on a level lot, this meticulously maintained home offers the perfect balance of privacy, outdoor space, and timeless charm. Designed for today&apos;s lifestyle, the thoughtfully crafted floor plan flows effortlessly from room to room, while the screened porch and expansive deck create seamless indoor-outdoor living, ideal for year-round entertaining and everyday family life. Move-in ready, the home has been lovingly cared for and thoughtfully updated with numerous quality improvements, including a new high-efficiency boiler and a full whole-house generator for ultimate peace of mind. Enjoy the very best of Darien, with award-winning schools, beautiful beaches and parks, a vibrant downtown filled with exceptional shopping and dining, and convenient access to Metro-North and major highways. This exceptional, turnkey home offers the lifestyle today&apos;s buyers are seeking-a rare opportunity not to be missed.",
